{"tid":1494882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位香港嘅加拿大人快啲登記做選民，逼加拿大政府正視香港問題","createTime":"2019-08-21T23:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T23:14:12.000Z","uid":223407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0042ae75e21fc066eaa340a16b95af5aa8a5d7e6","tid":1494882,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:06:46.000Z","msg":"選舉在即，今年法院仲要裁定唔俾海外公民投票係違憲。香港人要喺呢個多事之秋把握機會喺加拿大國會選舉行使投票權，將香港議題帶入議會/選舉上面，迫令政客表態支持香港民主同埋對一切反人道罪行表態同制裁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />靠你哋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CanadianHKvote/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCanadianHKvote%2F&d=qWTZpUodHfCf2bB0mbfn08ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=0aa54e6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CanadianHKvote/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NzYPzRL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNzYPzRL.png&h=383b12af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"163462ea8023145c0958fa4c7616117eda14136d","tid":1494882,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:13:34.000Z","msg":"推上去"},{"pid":"91443a3d690d38a26ce6f5994482872975fb8c85","tid":1494882,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"163462ea8023145c0958fa4c7616117eda14136d","tid":1494882,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:13:34.000Z","msg":"推上去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:13:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"08cee0d5925e4dcf5724a7b9b07011b11905b5df","tid":1494882,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:14:12.000Z","msg":"推"}]}